Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Being Here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's do an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:39.39,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finest Quality Refined Rice Flour\NDomestic Wet-land Glutinous Rice 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should we start with 200 grams\Nfor the sticky rice flour dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:45.60,SMR,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOD
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should we call it\N"chilled shiratama syrup"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crescent Moon was going to have a food stand\Nat the annual summer festival{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the shopping district.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This year, Grandpa let us decide\Nwhat would be on the menu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}March Town Shopping District\NMarch Town Festival\NSunday, July 28th
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To explain it simply,\Nthe way you make rice flour dumplings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Step one. Knead the rice flour in cold water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Step two. Roll into balls and boil in hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.47,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GIGGLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}AHAHA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? Simple, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? "Simple, right?" It's way too simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}EHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll go with 200 grams of rice flour\Nand about 160 cc of cold water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rice flour is sold\Nat the super market.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put the flour in a bowl and pour the water in\Na little at a time, mixing as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's mixed well,\Nput some muscle in it as you knead it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you put in too much water, it'll get sticky,\Nand make it hard to form into balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so stop when the dough has taken shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then roll the dough out\Ninto rod shapes with your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and rip them apart into bite-sized piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting the hang of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}KNEAD\NKNEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ROLL\NROLL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rice flour dumplings! This is Momo's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FWHAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}PUSH\NPUSH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SQUISH\NSQUISH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're doing good, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe it's a little big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, about this size?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too small?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TINY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More circular?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. They'll expand a bit\Nwhen we boil them, so that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When making large rice flour dumplings,\Nyou would put a little dent in them like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but today we're making smaller ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next we put them in boiling water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After two or three minutes,\Nthey'll come burbling up to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you keep them in the boiling water\Nfor another minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then transfer them to ice water,\Nwhich firms them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TA-DAA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SPRINGY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was so fast! And simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At first, let's just try it\Nwith sugar and soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so chewy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rice flour dumplings\Npass the taste test,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the challenge is the syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have matcha, right?\NPlum syrup, chilled sweet red bean soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so delicious with matcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But powdered matcha is expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I don't want to make each cup\Nmore than 300 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um, if we can get about 60 small dumplings\Nfrom 200 grams of rice flour...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:42.95,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HMMM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.45,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! How about cold milk tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's rich and sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That could be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, black tea leaves would be much cheaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we also put in black pearl tapioca?\NIt would make nice color accents!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}To defray the cost of the tapioca,\Ninstead of using disposable bowls and spoons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}we can gather spoons and bowls from our house,\NCrescent Moon, and Aunt Misaki's pub,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and just keep washing them,\Neven though it might be a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Oh, we can have Kiriyama do the washing!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good idea! Let's ask him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did a pretty good job with the dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You put them in ice water\Nto firm them up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And tapioca?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another fancy thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's pretty firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a type of starch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}THUMP THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it, it's actually really good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got a feeling the youngsters\Nwill really like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It should sell pretty well at a food stand.\NIt's a festival, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.33,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BRIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one was especially good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plum syrup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's refreshing and tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That plum syrup was made by Chiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? That's a nice smell from the plums.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}As soon as summer vacation started,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}we went to see Chiho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}She took me around the farm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WAG WAG WAG
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}WAHH
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Play with me. Woof-woof!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}She showed me Hana, and her puppies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Love! I love you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes while we talk,\NChiho would go silent and space out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ms. Satou said that even now, Chiho freezes up\Nwhen she sees a girl of middle school age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seeing someone of the same age\Nmakes all of her painful memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}come flooding back into her heart and mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently her body is resisting that\Nwith every strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Chiho is working hard here,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so that little by little,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she'll be able to talk\Nand act like she used to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what Ms. Satou told me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}CHIHO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chiho developed a fever in the evening,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so her mom dropped Sis and me\Noff at the station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Thank you so much for supporting Chiho."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her mom said that as she clasped my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She said, "Chiho and I\Nwill be doing our best here."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first step is making friends with animals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next is making friends\Nwith people older than you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The third step is making friends\Nwith people close to your age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even now, Chiho is fighting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll send her photos from the summer festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Photos of everyone enjoying the plum syrup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, I'll go visit her again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Crescent Moon here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about some sweet, chilled\Nrice flour dumpling syrup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Chilled\NRice Flour Dumpling Syrup\N300 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Milk Tea\NPlum Syrup\NSweet bean
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Chilled Ginger Drink\N100 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet and cold rice flour dumpling syrup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your plum syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some clean plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll take these back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PROMPT PROMPT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also 100 yen coins.\NI'll empty two rolls in here for change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PROMPT PROMPT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And dish cloths.\NI'll hang up the ones I washed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama is the best! He's so considerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for working you so hard, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, at least have a cool ginger drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The festival is a success.\NAnd we're selling like crazy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time doing something\Nlike this, so I'm kind of surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That it's pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama! Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Hey...\N- What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yo. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huh? Have you gotten way taller again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chiho made this plum syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's huge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}WHOA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma. Mikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delicious three-colored\Nrice flour dumplings here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would you like any?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. They're doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's a nice night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I love this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KA-CHING
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STUFFED
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:17.03,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TREMBLE\NTREMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It isn't even 7:00.\NWe made all this in no time at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I think we can easily sell the curry\Nthat's on the stove for dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curry is no good! We're a sweets shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're down to less than one box of dumplings!\NEven though we made a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's boil some more right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! We're out of syrup too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}EMPTY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Right when we're on a selling streak?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FWIP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SALESMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRACKLE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We still have soybean flour\Nand brown sugar syrup, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, boil some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hina, mind the store!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, buy us some ice. Ask the Takahashi boy\Nand he'll tell you where.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll knead the dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Kawamoto family, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being Here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Summer Vacation (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The March Town Festival was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.47,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COZY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should've prepared more syrup, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought we'd sell out by 7:00.\NSuch a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of shame, you spent too much on it\Nand were too generous with the portions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After working so hard drenched in sweat,\Nthis is our net profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call\N"going through great pains in vain"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really gets my blood pumping\Nwhen we're swarmed with customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}YEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all the people who stopped by,\Nwe sold lots of our usual sweets too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a loss leader is fine\Nwhen it comes to attracting customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like when you go to the supermarket\Nif they have milk on sale for 128 yen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or 100 grams of ham for 68 yen\Nor a can of tomatoes for 78 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course you buy other stuff\Nwhile you're there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom and grandma\Nwere both natural salesladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether they'd make something\Nsweet or sour, it didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There'd always be a line of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was really something.\NI thought that every time there was a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you girls would've seen it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.17,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.\NThe deep-fried kitty-cats and lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bags with the huge ribbons were so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They often said,\N"Spend effort, not money."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd help out by stuffing the bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did a great job for your first time out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you still need to work on sales and have\Na ways to go with finesse and insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you can give it\Nanother shot next year, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FWOHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have customers lined up,\Njust like Mom and Grandma did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}OHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think about the menu right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}STRETCH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FWOHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GRAB
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have entrance exams first.\NWhich schools are you applying to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have the summer term test tomorrow.\NDespite the summer vacation, it's a school day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you study for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, I did.\NI still have to study a little more though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it, Sis, how about jelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands have stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap it already!\NThe red bean pancake will dry out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Sorry, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHAKE\NSHAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHIVER\NSHIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!\NI can't be the homeroom teacher for 3A!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PANIC
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much to bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, too!\NThe menacing look of Takagi's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't have the confidence\Nto contend with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new homeroom teacher?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're entrusting the precious last semester\Nof the third year to a young teacher like that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is the school thinking?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WAHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! I'm still a newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may be a newbie, but I'm an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't physically be\Nthe homeroom teacher for two classes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch 90 students by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I've got my duties\Nas the head teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Besides, how long will this\Nongoing discussion with Takagi last?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. Getting her\Nto understand what she did is part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, no matter what else\Nwe say to her, it won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's already decided\Nnot to feel any guilt over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to spend all this time on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paying all this attention\Nto the person who caused the trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while the victim, Chiho Sakura,\Nnot only moved away because of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she isn't going to school yet over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-If she's unwilling to give in,\Neven if there was no malice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, after taking it this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't matter if there was ill will or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Komigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write it on her record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As her new homeroom teacher,\NI'll write it all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That she thinks she's always right\Nand is very aggressive towards other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That she's like the leader of the group,\Nbut causes major problems in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When somebody causes a problem,\Nthey need to take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There must be punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's wrong, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Kokubu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find a reason for why everyone\Nhas to put out effort and do their best?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well. I've been thinking a lot since it came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ATTENDANCE\NRECORDS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I racked my brains, but in the end,\Nto be honest, I came up blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And when I thought about it,\NI realized I never even had any doubts about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to make an effort,\Nbut I always assumed people had to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:20:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this time I thought making an effort\Nwas something you do for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'd been told that often enough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that I don't even remember\Nwho first said it or where I'd read that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've reached this age,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that phrase was true\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the longest time, I probably just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to become a better person\Nthan I was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we're suddenly talking about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to take long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was my last day\Nas your class's interim homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right now, I think you have a lot of anxiety\Nthat you don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You haven't done anything in your life yet,\Nso you don't know your own capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's the cause of your anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mr. Kokubu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You refuse to make an effort with anything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because you're scared of learning your own\Ncapacity and being disappointed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once you learn your own capacity, you at last\Nunderstand what it is you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you understand yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what you want to do\Nwill also become more clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once you do that, you'll at least be able\Nto get past your incredible anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can guarantee at least that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:22:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I was done with the test,\Nthat night, I made a lot of drawings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were so many colorful sweets swimming\Naround in my head and they wouldn't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, how long are you going to stay up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take your bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just leave the fan on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They all look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. These are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Vacation (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.47,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 42
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful and look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, how old were you\Nwhen you first
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.47,0:24:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to become\Na professional shogi player?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.60,0:24:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama! It's a beautiful day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.27,0:24:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like smooth stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.07,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's really adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:59.04,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ILLUSTRATION:\NAKIMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.15,0:24:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, look at the sweets\NHina thought up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.08,0:24:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are great!
